Restatement (Second) of Torts \u00a7 343.raw_text: Restatement (Second) of Torts § 343 (dangerous conditions on land)
Restatement (Second) of Torts \u00a7 343.proposition: Plaintiff also relies on recognized tort authorities, including Restatement (Second) of Torts § 343 (dangerous conditions on land) and § 314A (duty regarding conduct of third persons on premises), as guidance for the duties of possessors of land and operators of programs with respect to supervision and protection of invitees and children on their premises.
